00:00:47.940 --> 00:00:49.100
Let’s start with an easy thing!

00:00:49.300 --> 00:00:52.080
Pugna can hide Undying’s Tombstone to Astral

00:00:52.080 --> 00:00:55.080
to make it invulnerable for three and a half seconds.

00:00:55.080 --> 00:00:57.700
Three and a half seconds is a lot of time in Dota!

00:00:57.700 --> 00:01:02.020
You will have more than enough time to deal a lot of trouble to your enemies.

00:01:05.260 --> 00:01:06.380
And now something a bit harder!

00:01:06.900 --> 00:01:10.780
As you are going to learn, Rubick can be extremely effective versus Ember Spirit.

00:01:11.380 --> 00:01:13.840
Rubick steals Ember Spirit’s Fire Remnant

00:01:13.840 --> 00:01:16.600
and place up to three of it in any place of the map.

00:01:25.720 --> 00:01:29.340
After that Rubick has to steal any other skill from any other hero

00:01:29.340 --> 00:01:31.222
before Remnants will disappear.

00:01:31.780 --> 00:01:32.420
Wait a bit…

00:01:32.740 --> 00:01:36.740
Voila! Remnants are gone, but the overview they used to give us is still there!

00:01:36.740 --> 00:01:38.457
And it’s going to stay for the whole game!

00:01:38.460 --> 00:01:42.480
That’s the way we get free wards that cannot be destroyed.

00:01:42.980 --> 00:01:45.900
Besides that, Rubick can pull that trick a lot of times,

00:01:45.900 --> 00:01:49.200
and every time he can place three more Remnants on the map.

00:02:05.100 --> 00:02:07.800
Do you like Weaver? I like him very much!

00:02:07.800 --> 00:02:10.400
And I’ll share one interesting feature of this hero with you.

00:02:10.400 --> 00:02:12.195
If you’ll get Weaver an Aghanim's,

00:02:12.200 --> 00:02:15.760
you’ll be able to send your allies back in time for five seconds.

00:02:15.760 --> 00:02:17.880
Well, that’s not the feature – everybody knows it anyway.

00:02:18.360 --> 00:02:23.180
Feature is that this comeback in time don’t interrupt the abilities

00:02:23.180 --> 00:02:26.280
like Enigma’s and Witch Doctor’s Ults and stuff like that.

00:02:26.400 --> 00:02:29.780
Enigma makes Blink, casts Black Hole and comes back to where she was.

00:02:29.780 --> 00:02:31.840
The enemy is horrified and doesn’t understand what to do.

00:02:31.840 --> 00:02:33.263
Same goes for Witch Doctor.

00:02:33.263 --> 00:02:35.760
It works with other skills like that as well.

00:02:36.120 --> 00:02:38.660
Shadow Shaman’s Serpent, for example.

00:02:38.960 --> 00:02:41.480
But it’s not effective with Crystal Maiden at all.

00:02:41.480 --> 00:02:43.700
Her Ultimate works strictly around her,

00:02:43.700 --> 00:02:47.740
so if we’ll move her somewhere, Ultimate will follow her.

00:02:52.240 --> 00:02:53.320
Forth for today.

00:02:53.680 --> 00:02:57.860
You can save yourself from first lever Bloodseeker’s Ultimate by using flask.

00:02:57.860 --> 00:03:00.020
Just run and drink from the flask.

00:03:00.020 --> 00:03:04.560
It won’t stop its action. And you won’t lose a lot of health!

00:03:11.700 --> 00:03:12.480
