00:03:12.800 --> 00:03:16.880
There is one terrible bug-feature about Undying’s Tomb and Chen.

00:03:16.940 --> 00:03:20.000
Chen can entice zombies from the Tomb over his control.

00:03:20.180 --> 00:03:25.140
Zombies are quite dangerous, since they have 1000 HP unlike their original brothers.

00:03:25.140 --> 00:03:27.360
But they disappear when Tomb does…

00:03:27.600 --> 00:03:29.260
But that’s not the main point.

00:03:29.260 --> 00:03:31.620
After Chen entices at least one zombie,

00:03:31.620 --> 00:03:33.840
every time when Undying will place the Tomb,

00:03:33.840 --> 00:03:36.360
one of spawning zombies will belong to Chen.

00:03:36.880 --> 00:03:41.700
Therefore, if when you’re playing for Chen you’ll be enticing one or two zombie every time,

00:03:41.700 --> 00:03:46.900
after some time Tomb will become a real enemy for Undying and his team, instead of being his ally.

00:03:47.420 --> 00:03:50.200
And ten or so zombies with 1000 HP is not a joke!

